snippet.title: Love Exalt 8372 Trailer
snippet.description:
Love Exalt 8372 is a furry visual novel about a death game on a train. Read the minds of characters through minigames, choose which perspectives you want to see, and uncover the mysterious lore behind twelve unique characters.
